349
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shucks, Miss Mathilda. Thank you.</font>

350
00:20:23,580 --> 00:20:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Stay safe, Allen.</font>

351
00:20:25,630 --> 00:20:26,290
