00:20:31,170 --> 00:20:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aw, crap!</font>

355
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:35,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dogora?</font>

356
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And Pelomas?</font>

357
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uh, hi.</font>

358
00:20:41,710 --> 00:20:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here.</font>

359
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's for me?</font>

360
00:20:46,380 --> 00:20:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hmph! Don't say I never gave you nothin'!</font>

361
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That kid's a riot!</font>

362
00:20:56,380 --> 00:20:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And generous to boot!</font>

363
00:20:58,330 --> 00:20:58,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah!</font>

364
00:21:00,210 --> 00:21:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's get going, Allen.</font>

365
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Right.</font>

366
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allen.</font>

367
00:21:19,130 --> 00:21:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Manservant is only the first step for you.</font>

368
00:21:22,040 --> 00:21:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Work hard and you'll go places.</font>

369
00:21:24,330 --> 00:21:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah. I'll do my best!</font>

370
00:21:33,670 --> 00:21:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey! They're almost ready to leave!</font>

371
00:21:36,670 --> 00:21:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bye, son. Make me proud.</font>

372
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:42,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Come home if it gets too tough, okay?</font>

373
00:22:23,630 --> 00:22:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Goodbye, everybody.</font>

